descriptionHtml:
After some people complaining about being unable to create a nice female face i decided to make my own :)
Now you got the chance to start as Freya :D her real origin is still a riddle, she is waiting for you to solve it.
----------------------------------
You will start the Game in Riverwood with lvl 1 and 350 Gold added.

HOW TO INSTALL:
Simply copy the Savegame into your skyrim saves folder.
Located under Documents/mygames/skyrim/saves
---------------------------------

Required Mods:
!!Attention!!
Install this mods in the following order, otherwise you wont get her look.
---------------------------------
Apachii Sky Hair
Better females by Bella
High Quality Eyes
UNP Blessed Body (is higly recommended because of better face textures)
Mature skin texture and body for UNP (to get the natural beauty-look)
---------------------------------

Special thanks goes to the above mentioned Mods and to Corta for creating
Angelina Jolie Savegame
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22286

ATTENTION!
If somethings wrong with the savegame or if its corrupted pleasy comment and i will try to fix it as soon as possible.
.................................

This is my first upload so please dont be too disapointed if something doesnt work.
Im Austrian, sorry for English.
